text: Las Flores Partido is a partido of Buenos Aires Province in Argentina. The provincial subdivision has a population of about 23,000 inhabitants in an area of , and its capital city is Las Flores, which is from Buenos Aires. It is connected to the rest of the province by National Route 3 and Provincial Routes RP 30, RP 61 and RP 63. ==Economy== The economy of Las Flores partido is dominated by agriculture.
